Numpy: scientific computing package with arrays and matrices

-- Install
pip install numpy

if pip is not properly upgraded, first upgrade: pip install --user --upgrade pip

-- Functions
np.amax(array): find the maximum value of the array
np.amin(array): find the minimum value of the array
np.arange(low, high, interval): produce a series of numbers within the high-low bound, increasing by interval
np.empty(size): creates an array of given size filled with random numbers (faster than zeros or ones)
